'[Verse 1]\n[C]God sent His son they [F]called Him Jesus\n[C]He came to love [G]heal and forgive\n[C]He lived and died to [F]buy my pardon\n[C]An empty grave is [G]there to prove my Savior [C]lives\n\n[Chorus]\n[C]Because He lives I can [F]face tomorrow\n[C]Because He lives all [G]fear is gone\n[C]Because I know He [F]holds the future\nAnd [C]life is worth the [G]living just because He [C]lives\n\n[Verse 2]\n[C]How sweet to hold a [F]newborn baby\n[C]And feel the pride and [G]joy He gives\n[C]But greater still the [F]calm assurance\n[C]This child can face un[G]certain days because He [C]lives',
'C', 0, 80, '3/4', 'Verse1, Chorus, Verse2, Chorus', 1, TRUE),

